      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TECHNO KELLI (2) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight finishing 4th and beaten only 1.75 lengths (17.05). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Fast beginner suited by an inside draw. Can atone. BITTER FURY (5) was below best last time at Murray Bridge Straight (17.64) in a Invitation, finishing a 5 length fourth. Has two wins already from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. BLUE PRIDE (4) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Invitation at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m. Can hit the frame this time. MY MUM'S VALUE (1) showed plenty of dash to record a last start win. Hard to beat again.",
